    <!-- 2. WHAT IT IS -->
    <section class="section" aria-labelledby="what-title">
      <div class="container reveal">
        <p class="eyebrow">// Sector 01 &mdash; The pitch</p>
        <h2 id="what-title">What it is</h2>
        <div class="prose den-card">
          <p>Wrestling City Tactics is what happens when a tactics RPG learns to work the crowd. Every match plays out on a grid, turn by turn &mdash; position your wrestlers, set up the spot, and pick the moment the finish lands. Between bells, you&rsquo;re running the show: scouting talent, building a stable, and growing a roster of original personas with egos as big as their move sets. And because this is wrestling, winning is only half the job. Rivalries simmer, alliances crack, faces turn heel &mdash; and every result writes the next chapter of a city-wide storyline. The drama isn&rsquo;t a cutscene between fights. It&rsquo;s the campaign. Plan the match like a general. Book the aftermath like a promoter.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

