            <h3>Original Personas Only</h3>
            <p>No borrowed faces, no licensed legends &mdash; every wrestler in the city is an original creation with their own look, history, and in-ring philosophy. The gimmick isn&rsquo;t a costume; it&rsquo;s a strategy. Build around your stars, and the city learns their names.</p>
          </article>
