            <h3>Kayfabe Runs Deep</h3>
            <p>Wins and losses feed an unfolding drama of rivalries, betrayals, and heel turns. Stories spill out of the ring and across the city &mdash; and the smartest players book the match and the aftermath. Protect the kayfabe. Play the long con.</p>
